<% pageClass = "page-form"; %>
<% pageTitle = "Privacy Policy"; %>
<% layout("../layouts/boilerplate") %>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container legal-shell">
    <div class="page-hero-panel fade-up">
      <div class="section-kicker bg-white text-dark">Privacy</div>
      <h1 class="section-title text-white mb-2">How Homify handles the information people trust us with.</h1>
      <p class="mb-0 text-white-50">This page now matches the rest of the product instead of feeling like a disconnected screen.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section pt-0">
  <div class="container legal-shell">
    <article class="detail-card legal-card fade-up">
      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-2">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-soft mb-0">Homify is committed to protecting personal information. This policy explains what we collect, how we use it, and the general steps we take to safeguard it.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-2">2. Information we collect</h2>
        <p class="text-soft mb-2">We may collect information you provide directly, including:</p>
        <ul class="text-soft mb-0">
          <li>Email address and username</li>
          <li>Contact information</li>
          <li>Listing details and uploaded images</li>
          <li>Review and rating content</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-2">3. How we use information</h2>
        <ul class="text-soft mb-0">
          <li>Provide and improve platform functionality</li>
          <li>Process account actions and confirmations</li>
          <li>Send essential service-related updates</li>
          <li>Respond to support and safety issues</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-2">4. Data security</h2>
        <p class="text-soft mb-0">We use industry-standard security practices to reduce risk, including encrypted password handling and secure transfer of sensitive data.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-2">5. Third-party services</h2>
        <p class="text-soft mb-0">Homify uses external providers such as Cloudinary for image storage and MongoDB-related services for persistence. Those providers maintain their own policies and operational controls.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-2">6. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-soft mb-0">Questions about privacy can be directed to support@homify.com.</p>
      </section>
      <div class="panel-card">
        <strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2026
      </div>
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
